1 Month Ago The President of the Senate thereafter sought clarification from Moro as to whether the wife, who is the petitioner, is presently seeking judicial remedy before any court. In his response to Lawan, the lawmaker disclosed that there was no suit before any court of law on the matter. The petition was then referred to the Committee on Ethics, Privileges and Public Petition. 